t;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/20/3</guid><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 08:13:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-20 #3</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/20/2</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fd964e440e92e0137cf47005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;To the horror of the lifeboat's other members, Madonna loses her balance and falls on her face.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/20/2</guid><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 08:12:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-20 #2</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/20/1</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F2addab80e85c0137cedf005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Until his medical license was suspended, cosmetic surgeon Dr. Irwin Blumenfeld left many of his patients with the tragic side effect known as “buffalo nose.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/20/1</guid><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 08:11:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-20 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/20/0</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Ff2602260e6f70137ce50005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Tales of the Known&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/20/0</guid><pubDate>Fri, 20 Mar 2026 08:10:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-19 #5</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/19/4</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F8126b300cdd40137c56b005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Hey, Bob! So how’s death been treating you?”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/19/4</guid><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 08:09:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-19 #4</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/19/3</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F6df4aed0e92d0137cf47005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Whoa! Listen to that, Marge! ... I said that kid was playing a mean sax!”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/19/3</guid><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 08:08:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-19 #3</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/19/2</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fc01ceeb0ea240137cfba005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Expatriates, they migrated in the 1920s to Paris’s Left Bank, gathering in their favorite haunts and discussing the meaning of cream pies and big shoes. They were, in fact, the original Boclownians.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/19/2</guid><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 08:07:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-19 #2</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/19/1</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F02075ee0dcc90137caaf005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Oh, wow! How could you even think that, Wendy? Of course it’s your mind I’m attracted to!”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/19/1</guid><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 08:06:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-19 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/19/0</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fcfcb3060e9ee0137cf93005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“We've done it! They've linked up! … Man,
 Feldman must be freaking out—he even hates
spiders.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/19/0</guid><pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 08:05:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-18 #5</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/18/4</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fc0562f70cdd60137c56b005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Say ... now I’m starting to feel kinda warm!”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/18/4</guid><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 08:04:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-18 #4</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/18/3</link><description>&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2Fa4cfba90e85a0137cedf005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;In a barbarian faux pas that quickly cost him his life, Garth is caught drinking his gruel with pinky fingers extended.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/18/3</guid><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 08:03:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-03-18 #3</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/18/2</link><