e: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/03/18/0</guid><pubDate>Wed, 18 Mar 2026 08:00:00 -0400</pubDate></item></channel></rss>